Hello Guys, 

I have `df=DataFrame("Full Name" =&gt; ["john","Mike", "Ford"], "ID CTO" =&gt; 1:3)` then i want to do the following query:

`X=@from i in df begin
  @where i."Full Name" == "Mike"
  @select {i."ID CTO"}
  @ collect DataFrame`
end

 But i get an error. What i am doing wrong? I am always getting errors when my column names has spaces on it. 

How can i do it?

Thanks
